1
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:26,280
Your mother was murdered.

2
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:33,920
What?

3
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,359
Everything I say is true.

4
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,040
One time,

5
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,879
I... I was drinking with that corrupt official.

6
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:42,920
We happened to be discussing your poetry.

7
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,719
That wretched official said,

8
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:48,560
"What good is unmatched poetry,"

9
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,599
"when he doesn't even know"

10
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,640
"his own mother was murdered?"

11
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,480
"He's nothing but a pitiful wretch."

12
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,159
Say that again.

13
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,640
That's... That's what that wretched official said.

14
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,480
I wouldn't dare deceive Your Highness.

15
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,599
Who did it?

16
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,319
Who did it?!

17
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,760
I really don't know!

18
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:07,920
That... That's all the wretched official said.

19
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,159
I didn't dare to ask further.

20
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,439
Spare me, Your Highness!

21
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,080
Your Highness!

22
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:19,879
Old Gao.

23
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,879
Have him lead the way.

24
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,120
Go seal off the gold mine.

25
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,039
Yes, sir.

26
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,080
Old Feng.

27
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:30,599
The Yang'an County magistrate is involved in this.

28
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,280
Interrogate him the moment we get back.

29
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:34,680
All right, understood.

30
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,560
Wait for me at the county office.

31
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,280
I'm going after Zhang Yuancang.

32
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,319
Golden Guard Pan.

33
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:44,719
What crime have we committed?

34
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,960
Why keep us locked up like this?

35
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,680
It's already been so long.

36
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,560
You're detaining court officials without cause.

37
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:51,199
I will...

38
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:53,120
I will submit a memorial.

39
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,599
And impeach you before His Majesty.

40
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,639
Golden Guard Pan!

41
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,120
Did you hear me?

42
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,759
Without evidence,

43
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,039
even the Inspectorate

44
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,120
has no right to detain court officials.

45
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,439
Ning Chen is young and rash.

46
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,879
Don't let him drag you into recklessness.

47
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:10,520
And ruin your own future.

48
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:13,919
Nice wine.

49
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,400
You're back.

50
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,759
General Ning.

51
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,360
Everyone here is a court official.

52
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,879
Detaining us all here,

53
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,039
what exactly do you mean by this?

54
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:30,240
If you don't give us a proper answer,

55
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:32,759
I will report this to the court.

56
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,039
And demand justice.

57
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,080
Someone's going to die!

58
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,520
What are we going to do?

59
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,479
Ning Chen!

60
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,919
I'm the Prefect of Lingzhou, after all.

61
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,520
How dare you humiliate me like this!

62
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,560
I will petition the Emperor himself.

63
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,639
And demand justice!

64
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:00,400
Ning Chen.

65
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,360
Don't be rash.

66
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,439
Someone really will die!

67
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:04,960
That's right.

68
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,199
All of you, listen well!

69
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,280
Lingzhou Prefect Zhang Yuancang,

70
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,560
recruited vagrants,

71
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,960
illegally mined gold,

72
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:17,240
and had men pose as bandits to harm civilians.

73
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,000
His crimes are unpardonable.

74
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,240
He deserves death.

75
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,319
Ning Chen.

76
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:28,199
Do you have any proof of these claims?

77
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,240
You, you, you...

78
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:29,959
You're lying!

79
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,279
I... I didn't!

80
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,560
I've been wronged!

81
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,439
Wrongly accused!

82
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:36,000
I've already captured the bandit chief.

83
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:38,639
And the Yang'an magistrate is in my custody.

84
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,079
Lord Zhang.

85
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,839
Every single thing you've done

86
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,040
is enough to wipe out three generations of your clan.

87
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,040
Jin Wu is talking nonsense.

88
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,279
Don't believe him.

89
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,959
Jin Wu?

90
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,360
So you even know his name is Jin Wu.

91
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,680
Gave yourself away, didn't you?

92
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,160
He's done for now.

93
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,399
Illegally mining gold

94
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,639
means the mastermind must be high-ranking.

95
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,519
And immensely powerful.

96
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:10,000
If we escort them to the capital for trial,

97
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,759
they'll likely be silenced

98
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,800
before we even get there.

99
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,399
Then we'll try them right here.

100
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:19,160
I'll interrogate Zhang Yuancang myself.

101
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:20,600
You, Ning!

102
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,399
How dare you hold a private tribunal!

103
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,800
Even if I'm guilty,

104
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:27,560
that's for the Ministry of Justice to handle.

105
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,120
It's not your place!

106
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,040
Old Pan.

107
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,279
I understand.

108
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,879
His Majesty gave me the imperial sword.

109
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,759
to execute first and report later.

110
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,000
Wherever the imperial sword stands,

111
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:53,720
that is the court of law.

112
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,279
Lord Zhang.

113
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,240
Let's talk about the gold mine.

114
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,079
Gold mine?

115
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,199
What gold mine?

116
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,759
No! No!

117
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,319
Drag his lower half to feed the dogs.

118
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,399
Bring up the second corrupt official.

119
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,040
Dismember him.

120
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,560
What are you saying, Lord Zhang?

121
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:26,240
The Inspectorate doesn't use illegal torture.

122
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,839
I know you weren't the mastermind.

123
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:31,000
If I write up lighter charges,

124
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:33,519
there might still be a way out.

125
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,360
Ning Chen!

126
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,199
I thought you didn't use torture!

127
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,879
But this is a public trial, Lord Zhang.

128
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,480
Old Pan.

129
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,079
Keep it down.

130
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,560
I don't want to either.

131
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:47,079
But he won't confess honestly.

132
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:47,959
Won't talk?

133
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,639
Then behead him.

134
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,560
Don't be scared, Lord Zhang.

135
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,839
Where were we just now?

136
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,160
We were at...

137
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:11,000
at how there might be a way out.

138
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:11,879
Are you done talking?

139
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,160
Time to torture me now, right?

140
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,879
Not done, not done!

141
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,759
We're not finished yet!

142
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:22,800
My lord!

143
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,040
I'll confess everything!

144
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:25,439
It was Ma Kaicheng.

145
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,079
And who is Ma Kaicheng?

146
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,959
He's from the Left Chancellor's manor.

147
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,720
When he first came to Lingzhou,

148
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,160
he stayed at my residence.

149
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,879
When he came,

150
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,839
he brought several jianghu masters.

151
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,720
Those men,

152
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,720
each one skilled at finding hidden veins.

153
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,000
This gold ore

154
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,839
was discovered by those very men.

155
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,480
The Left Chancellor's manor,

156
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,800
were there any secret letters exchanged?

157
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,759
No, there weren't.

158
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,519
Ma Kaicheng only brought verbal messages.

159
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,639
If that's the case,

160
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:56,240
we can't convict the Left Chancellor.

161
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,199
Even if we convicted him,

162
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,680
he could push it onto Ma Kaicheng.

163
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,399
Or simply have Ma Kaicheng killed,

164
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,040
leaving no witness behind.

165
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,439
Then this Zhang Yuancang,

166
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,319
there's no point keeping him alive.

167
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:08,959
Useless.

168
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,160
I'm useful! I'm useful!

169
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:12,240
I still have the ledgers!

170
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:13,360
They record

171
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,759
all the gold refined throughout Lingzhou,

172
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:16,519
and also

173
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,839
every official in Lingzhou involved.

174
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,480
My lord!

175
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:22,480
I have this too!

176
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,639
An Inspectorate token.

177
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,879
It seems

178
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,919
they used the Inspectorate's identity

179
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:45,399
to ship gold to and from the capital.

180
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,840
How impressive.

181
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,159
We've even got a mole in the Inspectorate.

182
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,159
Once I find out who it is,

183
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,000
I'll kill him for sure.

184
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,000
Don't act rashly.

185
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,120
This matter is of grave importance.

186
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,480
Once we return to the capital,

187
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,080
we must investigate carefully.

188
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,320
Right.

189
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,159
Lord Zhang.

190
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:12,000
Now let's talk about my mother.

191
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,120
Jin Wu has already confessed.

192
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:18,399
He said you once told him

193
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,480
that my mother was murdered.

194
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:21,960
Who is this person?

195
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,159
That dog Jin Wu.

196
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,159
My lord.

197
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,559
Please, please don't kill me.

198
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,440
I'll tell you everything.

199
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,039
The one who killed your mother

200
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,039
was also Ma Kaicheng.

201
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:36,519
Go on.

202
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:37,720
Yes, yes, yes.

203
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:39,720
My lord.

204
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,399
The truth is, Ma Kaicheng

205
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,240
came precisely because of your mother.

206
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,279
Those wandering jianghu figures

207
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,879
were all just a cover I made up.

208
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,360
Eight years ago,

209
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:50,960
your mother found gold in Changshou Village.

210
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,360
She knew it belonged to the court,

211
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,159
so she was going to report it.

212
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,639
I knew this matter

213
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,440
was far beyond what I could handle.

214
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,679
So I informed the Left Chancellor.

215
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:04,000
Ma Kaicheng was sent by the Left Chancellor

216
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,279
to silence my mother.

217
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,279
Why didn't you tell the truth earlier?

218
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:14,039
I feared you'd lose it and kill me!

219
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:14,639
Oh, right.

220
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:15,600
That's only the first part.

221
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,360
There's a second.

222
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,919
Ma Kaicheng controls the entire gold mine.

223
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,480
I'm only in charge of picking the men

224
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,519
and arranging transport.

225
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,080
I know nothing about the rest.

226
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,240
The Left Chancellor.

227
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,600
The Left Chancellor again.

228
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:29,120
Old Pan.

229
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,360
Keep interrogating him.

230
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,840
I'm going after Ma Kaicheng now.

231
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:33,600
Chen.

232
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:34,600
Calm down.

233
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,200
I understand how you feel right now,

234
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:37,759
but right now,

235
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:38,960
you must hold yourself back.

236
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,080
We have more important matters at hand.

237
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,240
Bring those three up here.

238
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:52,559
Kneel.

239
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,240
Kneel!

240
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,120
Well played.

241
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,399
You actually dared to set me up.

242
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,120
For scum like you,

243
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:04,399
do you think we'd play it straight?

244
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:06,440
Chen.

245
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:07,759
The most important thing now

246
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,399
is what to do with these men.

247
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:12,759
Post a notice.

248
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:17,600
Behead Zhang Yuancang and his men publicly.

249
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,320
General!

250
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:25,000
I've told you everything I know!

251
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,600
Take them away.

252
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,320
Take them all away.

253
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,440
My lord!

254
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,960
Ning Chen.

255
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,440
You little brat, have you lost your mind?

256
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:38,320
Kill them and we lose all our witnesses.

257
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,240
Deceiving the heavens to cross the sea.

258
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:43,799
Secretly marching on Chencang.

259
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:50,639
You clever boy.

260
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,200
I get what you mean.

261
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:55,399
But have you considered

262
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,759
this is deceiving the emperor. It'll get us killed.

263
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,720
Circumstances leave no choice.

264
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,840
I'll bear all the consequences alone.

265
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,039
I'll bear them with you.

266
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:23,159
Chen.

267
00:12:23,759 --> 00:12:25,840
Where do we hide them now?

268
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:29,080
Hand them over to Jiang Zhengyang.

269
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,919
Jiang Zhengyang?

270
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,080
He's an upright man.

271
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,320
The lead on the gold mine

272
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,240
he was the one who provided it.

273
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:39,519
Got it.

274
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,000
Old Pan.

275
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,159
Keep this under wraps.

276
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,639
Find a few reliable brothers,

277
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,840
and locate Ma Kaicheng.

278
00:12:46,679 --> 00:12:48,039
If the Left Chancellor catches wind,

279
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,240
he'll silence him for sure.

280
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,600
Everything else

281
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,120
can wait till we return to the capital.

282
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:53,960
Don't worry.

283
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,080
Leave it to me.

284
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:57,720
Chen.

285
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,759
Once this is done,

286
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:01,240
we'll be heading to the battlefield.

287
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:02,639
Are you

288
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:04,320
up to it?

289
00:13:07,159 --> 00:13:07,679
I'm fine.

290
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,879
You stubborn brat, always acting tough.

291
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,120
Get some good rest these next few days.

292
00:13:13,639 --> 00:13:14,200
Ahead of us,

293
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,840
there's a great battle awaiting.

294
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,440
Right.

295
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:37,559
You surely know

296
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,399
that I'm not really your son.

297
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,840
But since I now inhabit this body,

298
00:13:45,519 --> 00:13:48,080
I ought to call you Mother.

299
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,440
Maybe I've been in this world too long,

300
00:13:55,159 --> 00:13:56,200
but I feel more and more

301
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,519
that I truly am your son,

302
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,720
Ning Chen.

303
00:14:01,759 --> 00:14:02,600
When I learned

304
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,919
that you were murdered,

305
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:08,840
the pain made it hard to breathe.

306
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,320
Once my mind cleared,

307
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:15,360
I had only one thought:

308
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,480
to avenge you.

309
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:27,559
Rest assured,

310
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,440
those who ever harmed you,

311
00:14:31,679 --> 00:14:32,960
I won't spare a single one.

312
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:35,840
No matter how high their station,

313
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,159
or how great their power.

314
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,279
Mother,

315
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,600
watch closely from the other side.

316
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,240
After this is done,

317
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:53,639
the name Ning Chen

318
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:56,360
will echo across the realm.
